{"tid":1980323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團結香港：應簡化程序加快推展《明日大嶼》","createTime":"2020-04-20T04:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T05:15:53.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb8d9de3582d054f19d6c8bc3f7b31304657cb3","tid":1980323,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"團結香港基金建議政府加快目前的土地開發項目<br />\n20.04.2020 11:36<br />\n<br />\n團結香港基金發表土地房屋政策研究報告，指本港私樓供應量去年出現斷崖式下跌後，預測未來五年的私樓供應會繼續在谷底排徊，每年平均只有約1.6萬個單位，形成類似「地陷」的格局。基金亦預計，未來四年公營房屋供應量每年平均約兩萬個，較《長遠房屋策略》定下的供應目標少三成二。<br />\n<br />\n基金建議，<span style=\"color: gold;\">政府應加快現時的土地開發項目，及實施大規模填海計劃，並重新檢視、評估及簡化土地發展的行政程序</span>，增加房屋供應。基金亦建議，政府建立一站式公開平台，向公眾披露各個公屋項目的進度，並重新成立《長遠房屋策略》督導委員會，檢視房屋需求的推算方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282066&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282066%26csid%3D261_341&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=2c88b678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282066&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"895ba5e8b60648bcd050c34dde84b57833c46398","tid":1980323,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"團結香港：應盡快瓜分香港庫房"},{"pid":"6fe6e5cee4d141a08feca1feb4df78ef7b8c61b6","tid":1980323,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.